	"metadata":{
		"frontmatter":{},
		"version":"1.0-1.0"
	},
	"nodes":[
		{
			"color":"1",
			"height":60,
			"id":"root",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"大型语言模型 (LLM) 构建与强化学习 (Karpathy 教程)",
			"type":"text",
			"width":400,
			"x":-187,
			"y":-851
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":60,
			"id":"intro",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"一、引言：\n对话界面背后发生了什么？",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":-788,
			"y":-691
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":60,
			"id":"pretrain",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"二、第一阶段：\n从互联网下载文本，训练基础模型",
			"type":"text",
			"width":350,
			"x":-201,
			"y":-689
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":60,
			"id":"sft",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"三、第二阶段：\n监督微调 (SFT)，让模型学会对话",
			"type":"text",
			"width":350,
			"x":355,
			"y":-688
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":60,
			"id":"psychology",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"四、大模型的\"心理特征\"\n幻觉、推理与工具使用",
			"type":"text",
			"width":350,
			"x":-1289,
			"y":-223
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":60,
			"id":"rlhf",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"五、第三阶段：\n强化学习与人类反馈 (RL + HF)",
			"type":"text",
			"width":350,
			"x":-574,
			"y":-226
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":60,
			"id":"future",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"六、面向未来：\n多模态、长程规划与新范式",
			"type":"text",
			"width":350,
			"x":4,
			"y":-233
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":60,
			"id":"usage_ecosystem",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"七、模型使用与开源生态",
			"type":"text",
			"width":350,
			"x":579,
			"y":-232
		},
		{
			"color":"2",
			"height":60,
			"id":"summary",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"八、总结：\n当我们与 ChatGPT 对话时，\n究竟在与什么对话？",
			"type":"text",
			"width":400,
			"x":1138,
			"y":-230
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":100,
			"id":"intro_process",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"LLM 构建流程概述：\n1. 预训练 (Pre-training)\n2. 监督微调 (SFT)\n3. 强化学习 (RL)",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":-785,
			"y":-580
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":120,
			"id":"pretrain_data",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"2.1 数据收集与过滤\n- 来源: Common Crawl, The Pile, RefinedWeb\n- 清洗: 去噪、去重、去 HTML\n- 过滤: 语言、恶意、隐私 (PII)\n- 规模: 数 TB ~ 十几 TB",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":-429,
			"y":-573
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":100,
			"id":"pretrain_tokenization",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"2.2 分词 (Tokenization)\n- 目标: 文本 -> Token 序列\n- 方法: BPE (Byte Pair Encoding)\n- 词表大小: GPT-4 ~100k\n- 输出: Token ID 序列",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":-130,
			"y":-572
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":140,
			"id":"pretrain_training",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"2.3 核心: 自回归语言模型训练\n- 任务: 预测下一个 Token\n- 模型: Transformer (数十/百层)\n- 损失: 交叉熵\n- 成本: 巨大算力、工程、资金\n- 结果: 基础模型 (Base Model)",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":177,
			"y":-572
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":80,
			"id":"sft_why",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"3.1 为何需要 SFT?\n- Base Model ≠ 对话助手\n- 需注入对话/指令风格\n- 缺乏安全合规",
			"type":"text",
			"width":250,
			"x":224,
			"y":-570
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":100,
			"id":"sft_data",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"3.2 构建对话数据\n- 格式: (用户问题, 理想回答)\n- 来源: 人工编写、模型生成+筛选\n- 规模: 几十万 ~ 上百万条",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":513,
			"y":-569
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":100,
			"id":"sft_how",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"3.3 底层实现: 再一次自回归\n- 训练集: 对话数据\n- 目标: 预测对话中的下一 Token\n- 特殊标识: <system>, <user>, <assistant>\n- 结果: 初步可用的对话模型",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":827,
			"y":-570
		},
		{
			"color":"6",
			"height":60,
			"id":"sft_limitations",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"SFT 后仍存缺陷:\n幻觉、不礼貌、无法拒答等",
			"type":"text",
			"width":270,
			"x":516,
			"y":-443
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":140,
			"id":"psych_hallucination",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"4.1 幻觉 (Hallucination)\n- 原因: 下一 Token 预测无法分辨事实与风格，易编造。\n- 缓解:\n  - 更多上下文\n  - 强化\"不知道\"\n  - 引入工具",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":-1512,
			"y":-90
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":160,
			"id":"psych_tool_use",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"4.2 工具使用 (Tool Use)\n- 目的: 克服模型知识局限\n- 方式: 开放 API 接口\n  - 搜索引擎 (提供最新信息)\n  - Python 解释器 (计算验证)\n- 实现: 特殊 Token (<search_start>) 触发系统调用",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":-1151,
			"y":-88
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":120,
			"id":"psych_cot",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"4.3 多步推理 (CoT)\n- 原因: Token 即计算力，复杂问题需分解\n- 方法: Chain-of-Thought (逐步写思路)\n- 效果: 提高复杂任务 (数学、逻辑) 准确率",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":-801,
			"y":-89
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":120,
			"id":"rlhf_why",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"5.1 为何需要 RL?\n- 目的: 自主试错，探索更优解\n- 机制: 生成多方案 -> 评估 -> 强化正确/惩罚错误\n- 提升: 推理能力 (数学、编程)\n- 类比: AlphaGo 自对弈",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":-760,
			"y":-91
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":100,
			"id":"rlhf_verifiable",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"5.2 可验证 vs 不可验证\n- 可验证: 数学、代码 (有标准答案)\n  -> RL 效果显著\n- 不可验证: 写作、艺术 (主观评估)",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":-452,
			"y":-90
		},
		{
			"color":"4",
			"height":100,
			"id":"rlhf_reward_model",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"不可验证 -> 人类反馈 (HF)\n- Reward Model: 模拟人类偏好打分\n- 训练: 标注 A vs B 优劣\n- 风险: Reward Hacking",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":-448,
			"y":46
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":100,
			"id":"rlhf_limitations",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"5.3 RLHF 局限性\n- 好处: 模拟人类审美\n- 局限: 易过度拟合 Reward Model 漏洞\n- 应用: 通常只做少量步骤改进",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":-148,
			"y":-90
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":120,
			"id":"future_multimodal",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"6.1 多模态\n- 目标: 处理文本、图像、音频\n- 方法:\n  - 图像 -> Patch Token\n  - 音频 -> 频谱 Token\n- 应用: 看图说话、理解音频",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":-186,
			"y":-87
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":120,
			"id":"future_agent",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"6.2 长程任务与 Agent\n- 目标: 执行复杂长期任务\n- 框架: 多轮 Agent\n  - 管理上下文\n  - 调用工具\n  - 循环迭代",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":130,
			"y":-89
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":100,
			"id":"future_online",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"6.3 训练模式拓展\n- 在线学习: 推理阶段微调\n- 优点: 持续进化\n- 风险: 内容审计、安全",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":449,
			"y":-89
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":140,
			"id":"usage_where",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"7.1 获取途径\n- 闭源: OpenAI, Anthropic, Google (API/网站)\n- 开源: LLaMA, DeepSeek, HF (本地/社区)\n- 平台: 云厂商, Inference 提供商",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":398,
			"y":-91
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":100,
			"id":"usage_types",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"7.2 Base vs Instruct/Chat\n- Base: 纯自回归，适合研究\n- Instruct/Chat: 微调后对话风格",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":707,
			"y":-91
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":80,
			"id":"usage_local",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"7.3 本地部署\n- 方法: 蒸馏、量化 (4/8bit)\n- 要求: 高端 GPU / Apple Silicon",
			"type":"text",
			"width":280,
			"x":1019,
			"y":-89
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":200,
			"id":"summary_process",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"对话系统内部流程:\n1. 输入文本 -> Token 序列\n2. 结合上下文 -> 输入模型\n3. 模型 (预训练+SFT+RL) 自回归生成 Token\n4. (可选) 调用工具 -> 更新上下文\n5. 输出 Token -> 文本回答",
			"type":"text",
			"width":350,
			"x":976,
			"y":-88
		},
		{
			"color":"3",
			"height":140,
			"id":"summary_metaphor",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"text":"心理比喻:\n- SFT: 模仿\"教师\" (标注者)\n- RL: 注入推理习惯 + 纠错\n- 局限: 继承盲点，非完美",
			"type":"text",
			"width":300,
			"x":1376,
			"y":-90
		}
	]
}